   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 1 of Nero Claudius Caesar Augustus Germanicus Imperator, Choiak 29. Heras, wife of Aunes, son of Harthotes and her mother Taesis have paid for the pig tax of the village Theadelphia for the same year on account six obols."</ab>
